body.name: TISHLED Wireless Gaming Mouse Tri-Mode 2.4Ghz/Bluetooth 5.2/Wired USB-C with Two Scroll Wheels RGB LED Backlit 4-Level DPI Rechargeable Ergonomic Optical Mice for Computer/Laptop/Office/Gamer, Black
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Tuesday, February 13. Order within 1 hr 22 mins
features: [Tri-Mode Connection: 2.4G/BT5.2/USB-C] - Powerful 3-mode connection supports Wireless 2.4GHz / Bluetooth 5.2 / Wired USB Type-C. You can connect up to 3 bluetooth devices, 1 wireless 2.4GHz device and 1 wired device. Connect and switch devices easily with the Mode Switch Button on the left side. Working distance up to 10m.

[Adjustable RGB Lighitng Effects & 4-Level DPI] - The illuminated mouse has up to 11 RGB lighting effects. Press middle button and back button to switch the lighitng effects or turn on/off the light. Adjustable 4 levels DPI (1200/1600/2000/2400) that allow you to freely control the mouse speed and adjusts the sensitivity of the mouse. Default 1200 DPI. Press DPI +/- button to adjust and the light will flash the corresponding color (1200 red, 1600 green, 2000 blue, 2400 yellow).

[Ergonomic Design & Two Scroll Wheels] - The ergonomic mouse designed for right-handed user, wider palm and thumb rest provides comfortable support, reduces the pressure and tension brought by long-time work to the hand. With the middle scroll wheel and the side scroll wheel, you can easily roll up, down, left and right. More efficient during using wireless mouse for AutoCAD, Revit, Excel and Adobe graphic design software etc. (Note: If side scroll function isn't working, please download the mouse driver)

[Rechargeable & 9 Buttons Programmable] - Built-in 800mAh Li-polymer rechargeable battery, the mouse can be easily recharged via the supplied USB-C cable. 3 hours quick fully charged can be used continuously for about 53 hours. RGB LED lighting will remind you to charge when flashing red light. All 9 buttons are programmable, can be customized by driver.

[1-Year Warranty & Wide Compatibility] - This triple mode optical mouse is compatible with Win, Mac OS, iOS, Android, Linux, Chrome OS systems. Support PC, laptop, Mac, smartphone, iPad and tablet. Our products provide 30 days unconditional refund and 12-month worry-free warranty. And please feel free to contact us if you have any questions.
